{"tid":1383100,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"建議今星期勇武休息，讓和理非全面進場","createTime":"2019-07-29T15:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T07:19:11.000Z","uid":55257,"like":86,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"552c6b4b262c581af4b5b9d38999479d46b98293","tid":1383100,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:30:03.000Z","msg":"我建議呢星期勇武休息，讓和理非全面進場<br />\n<br />\n7.27及7.28的行動其實不算成功，勇武辛苦完一輪卻沒有造成光復運動的突破，反而去到一個臨界點是，一群和理非因前線傷亡慘重有所動搖，有聲音不忍再有人受傷而呼籲抗爭暫停休息，尤其警狗大幅提昇武力的不利因素下。面對連續數星期的受傷畫面，和理非一群顯然變得相當疲累。<br />\n<br />\n而且，7.28對警狗的討伐有失策的地方，進攻退守的戰略還需詳細研究，更發現有許多未有心理準備上前線的義士，面對速龍狗的突襲會顯得不知所措，也是造成多人受傷被捕的主因。<br />\n<br />\n因此小弟不才，呼籲勇武今星期休息：<br />\n<br />\n1. 救援被捕義士，組織被捕法律上的支援<br />\n2. 補充物資<br />\n3. 復完身體，包括衝突後的創傷後遺症<br />\n4. 讓和理非一群有所休息<br />\n5. 思考如何進退有道<br />\n<br />\n勇武休息，和理非當然要全面上場：<br />\n<br />\n1. 出席所有集會，包括罷工！<br />\n2. 繼續文宣工作，包括對家人教導<br />\n3. 許多地邊連農牆失修，必須重建，加強香港人「思想教育」<br />\n4. 多討論下一步行動，如果突破現時的樽頸位<br />\n<br />\n我希望做到是勇武義士可以休養生息，給時間讓文宣工作繼續發酵，爭取和理非一群更多的支持！"},{"pid":"3e5b3716b51b5e7bd5b979699926f741bb85715f","tid":1383100,"uid":217323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:31:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca8209b63ea0ecf50a3434a4cf5b7e55e7cff4dd","tid":1383100,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:34:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"69a821db6677b22e2fd95d7f3b5e24995c6b3680","tid":1383100,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:34:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32c22413dc241fdd772bba31e0037ac5f2e02f23","tid":1383100,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:38:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6053a039b3af95b3539d7bff9da043fa07beab2","tid":1383100,"uid":269681,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:40:21.000Z","msg":"其實同意 小弟既媽媽都係和理非黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔忍心睇到佢次次行動都睇港台睇到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本身佢已經有少少情緒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 我真係唔係搞分化 我只係想出黎分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下次有咩發小弟都會同大家出黎發"},{"pid":"89105a732554170c6a8d598fcf3babaa2d52b743","tid":1383100,"uid":270078,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:44:27.000Z","msg":"push, we always support Frontline. Just don't waste your life at this moment!"},{"pid":"9a5d5f1ada90e054602bd5ca3a3ff85e5fcf791a","tid":1383100,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:49:34.000Z","msg":"繼續支持光復香港運動！"},{"pid":"1d69d8365c4ec5ae0b71e171039e863606b4e455","tid":1383100,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:18:51.000Z","msg":"繼續支持光復香港運動！"},{"pid":"75a2359199e68b531bc455b30acb153c98d69b63","tid":1383100,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:27:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbaa3ef7126e09fd9501f4b61db9ff2727aa2644","tid":1383100,"uid":283182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:33:27.000Z","msg":"同意 推!"},{"pid":"5b3f87cc7d82d318bb9a6baaf3a1127464af58b5","tid":1383100,"uid":26705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:40:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7488cd033b0fa591deeff12cd3ab48c9bd68d037","tid":1383100,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:43:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d60880d87025345237a59dd977b685cb665581ed","tid":1383100,"uid":88141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:46:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"252b3f6590ab29a14ef8f82674e864130134c506","tid":1383100,"uid":273157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:46:25.000Z","msg":"運動已元氣大傷，必須休息，如果唔係會極速收皮"},{"pid":"5701f6366f60a157a028a5aefb901462be93e153","tid":1383100,"uid":115977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:48:23.000Z","