08f241e4abf1cd1072d43f","tid":1383100,"uid":272057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T07:19:11.000Z","msg":"[repost]文宣組全面入場，連儂牆後另一大計<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390414\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390414</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}